{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_05_01_short",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 新曲のジャケット撮影 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――I-UNITYが終了してしばらく経ち",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Before long I-UNITY ended",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "新曲のジャケット撮影を、私が中心になって進める？\n……どういうことなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Should I take the lead in the new song's CD cover shooting?\n…What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。新曲の『SUNNY PEACE for\nYou and Me！』なんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It's for the new song‚ \"SUNNY PEACE for You and Me!\"…\nI thought that having the members come up with it themselves",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "メンバー自ら考える方が曲に込めた想いを今までより\nもっと強くファンに伝えられるんじゃないかと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "might allow them to convey their feelings in the song\neven more strongly to the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、それでMV撮影はさくらちゃんに任せたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So you left the MV shooting to Sakura-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私でいいの？\nさくらちゃんはリーダーだから、ともかく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ is that okay ?\nSakura-chan is the leader‚ after all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはサニピでも星見プロでも\nみんなのまとめ役をやってくれていますし、適任ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ whether it's at Suny Peace or Hoshimi Prods.‚ You've always been\nthe one who brings everyone together‚ so you're the right person for the job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、年長者だからなんとなくそうなってるだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ it's probably just because I'm the oldest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、遙子さんはコミュニケーション力があって\nチームをまとめるのがうまいと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Haruko-san‚ you have excellent communication skills‚\nand you're good at leading a team.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だから、サニピのみんなの意見や撮影スタッフの能力を\nうまく引き出せるって期待してるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I expect you to bring out the opinions of the Sunny Peace\nand the abilities of the filming staff effectively.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}